com.hotmail.joatin37.jcore.landmanagement

Class LandHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hotmail.joatin37.jcore.landmanagement.LandHandler

  • public abstract class LandHandler
extends Object
    Your plugin should extend this class instead of the JavaPlugin class. This class brings all functions of the JavaPlugin class, and some additional functions to make the interaction with JTown easier.
    Since:
    1.0.0
    Author:
    Joatin
    See Also:
    JavaPlugin, ICore
